# Carbonara

## Ingredients

- Pasta
- Pork belly
– parmesan
– 2 eggs
– salt
– pepper


## Instructions

– Fry the port belly until crispy and set aside.
- Add salt to the water and bring to boil.
- Add pasta and cook until al dente.
– Toss the cooked pasta to bowl containing grated parmesan, pepper and mixed egg yolk.
– Stir vigorously.
– Enjoy!
